    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-tag">The problem</span>
      <h2>Every USB-C cable looks the same. They are not.</h2>
      <p>Your drawer is full of identical-looking cables. Some charge at full speed, some crawl. Some carry video, some can barely handle a mouse. The connector tells you nothing. And the cable that worked last month might be the one that has started misbehaving today.</p>
    </div>
