      <div class="problem-card"><span class="label usb4">USB4</span><div class="spec">40 Gbps, 100W</div><p>Fast data, good charging. Handles most displays and external SSDs without issues.</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><span class="label tb">Thunderbolt 4</span><div class="spec">40 Gbps, 240W</div><p>Full speed data, maximum charging, dual 4K displays. The cable your dock needs but you cannot tell by looking.</p></div>
