<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-tag">Features</span>
      <h2>Plain answers for cables that all look the same.</h2>
      <p>WhatCable reads the USB-C and USB Power Delivery details macOS already exposes, then turns them into useful labels, charging diagnostics, and port-by-port device context.</p>
    </div>
