      <article class="feature"><div class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg></div><h3>Charging bottlenecks</h3><p>See whether the cable, charger, or Mac is limiting the current charge rate, with the negotiated power profile highlighted.</p></article>
